# Founder ship loop (mandatory for box deploys)

Use when shipping code to the MS-S1, touching `scripts/deploy*`, `scripts/ship-patch*`, `scripts/box-*`, or `post-update.sh`.

## Default command (do not improvise deploy)

```powershell
cd C:\Users\ankur\curxor-os
.\scripts\ship-patch.ps1 -Quick          # daily dashboard patches
.\scripts\ship-patch.ps1                 # typecheck + qa:local + deploy
.\scripts\ship-patch.ps1 -OpsSmoke       # + bridge smoke on box
```

**Do not** raw `scp`/`rsync` to `/opt/curxor` unless recovery (see runbook). **Do not** call `deploy-to-box.ps1` directly except `-SkipPack` recovery.

## Agent obligations after code changes

1. **Gate** ‚Äî typecheck must pass; full `qa:local` before merge/wave ships (not required for `-Quick` hotfixes).
2. **Deploy** ‚Äî run `ship-patch.ps1` (agent runs it; do not tell user to run unless blocked on sudo/password).
3. **Verify** ‚Äî confirm `cat /opt/curxor/.deploy-stamp` matches expected commit; `ssh curxor "bash /opt/curxor/scripts/box-smoke.sh"` if deploy smoke raced restart.
4. **Commit** ‚Äî laptop `git commit` only after gate + box green.
5. **package.json / lockfile changed** ‚Äî deploy warns; run `sync-node-deps-to-box.ps1` (+ `sync-swc-to-box.ps1` if node_modules came from Windows) or `ship-patch.ps1 -SyncDeps`.
6. **Ops keys to box** ‚Äî `.\scripts\push-ops-env-to-box.ps1` (laptop `config/local/ops-digital.env` ‚Üí `/etc/curxor/digital.env`).
7. **Never** commit `config/local/ops-digital.env`, `.env.local`, or `.deploy-stamp`.

## Passwordless deploy (installed on box)

- One-time bootstrap: `.\scripts\box-install-deploy-sudo-override.ps1`
- Verify: `ssh curxor "sudo -n /opt/curxor/scripts/verify-deploy-sudo-override.sh"`
- On-box apply: `sudo /opt/curxor/scripts/box-apply-deploy.sh` (exact path ‚Äî not `sudo bash ‚Ä¶`)

## CRLF (Windows ‚Üí Linux)

- `.gitattributes` forces `*.sh` LF in git; ad-hoc scp still needs strip.
- Use `.\scripts\copy-script-to-box.ps1` for single scripts.
- **Never** put `sed 's/\r$//'` inside PowerShell **double-quoted** SSH strings (`\r` becomes real CR).
- Deploy strips script dirs only: `scripts/`, `pillar-4-dashboard/scripts/`, `pillar-2-engine/`.

## Recovery

| Symptom | Action |
|---------|--------|
| Deploy incomplete | `ssh -t curxor sudo /opt/curxor/scripts/box-apply-deploy.sh /tmp/curxor-deploy.tar.gz` |
| CRLF / `log() {` syntax error | strip script dirs then `sudo bash /opt/curxor/scripts/post-update.sh` |
| engine build failed offline | `.\scripts\sync-node-deps-to-box.ps1 -ThenBuild` |

